**Work Request Agent** is an intelligent agent integrated into the PMM (Plant Maintenance) application, designed to simplify and automate the creation of Work Requests in Business Central.
The Agent is available exclusively in **SaaS BC 28 (and later)** environments.
<br>

## What it does

* captures work requests directly from **received emails**

* automatically identifies the affected **machine and maintenance point**

* extracts the **problem description** and any **planned dates/times**

* automatically generates the **Work Request** in Business Central

* sends a **structured confirmation** to the requester with the details of the created request
<br>

## Why it matters

* reduces manual user activities

* speeds up the process of reporting and managing maintenance interventions

* ensures traceability and standardization of work requests
<br>

## Usage costs
Using the Work Request Agent is designed to be efficient: each processed request requires on average about **25 Copilot credits**, with variations depending on the complexity of the content.